'''ListenBrainz'''是一个免费开源项目，用以收集和保存用户收听音乐的习惯。所有的数据都是开放和可共享的，付费后也可用于商业用途。ListenBrainz由管理[[MusicBrainz|MusicBrainz]]的[[MetaBrainz基金会|MetaBrainz基金会]]运营。

ListenBrainz可以连接{{le|Music Player Daemon}}、[[Spotify|Spotify]]、[[Rhythmbox|Rhythmbox]]等音乐服务或播放器，也可导入[[Last.fm|Last.fm]]数据。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Singh |first1=Param |last2=Kamlesh |first2=Dutta |last3=Kaye |first3=Robert |last4=Garg |first4=Suyash |title=Music Listening History Dataset Curation and Distributed Music Recommendation Engines Using Collaborative Filtering |url=https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-30577-2_55 |journal=Lecture Notes in Electrical Engineering |date=24 September 2019 |volume=605 |pages=623–632 |access-date=13 February 2021 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327001026/https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-30577-2_55 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yadav |first1=Naina |last2=Singh |first2=Anil |title=Bi-directional Encoder Representation of Transformer model for Sequential Music Recommender System |journal=Forum for Information Retrieval Evaluation |date=December 2020 |pages=49–53 |url=https://dl.acm.org/doi/abs/10.1145/3441501.3441503 |access-date=13 February 2021}}</ref>ListenBrainz可以根据这些数据来推荐内容。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Porter |first1=Alastair |title=Playlists and personalised recommendations in ListenBrainz |url=https://blog.metabrainz.org/2020/12/24/playlists-and-personalised-recommendations-in-listenbrainz/ |website=MetaBrainz Blog |publisher=MetaBrainz Foundation |access-date=13 February 2021 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412012407/https://blog.metabrainz.org/2020/12/24/playlists-and-personalised-recommendations-in-listenbrainz/ }}</ref>

